  to Q1 2027. NOTE: this is a job\, not a grant or fellowship. Application 
 deadline Monday\, 8 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Exygy\nLocation: Remote\, 
 United States\nAward: Paid role: $97\,750-$132\,250 per year for a tempora
 ry engagement. No application fee.\nDuration: Temporary engagement Q3 2026
  to Q1 2027\n\nMore: https://exygy.com/careers/?utm_source=artificialnouve
